Elsie (Disclaimer)

Laura Mullen





Isn’t my invention
She’s really a real
“Character” her father
Art in advertising or
Urology but everything
Absolutely everything
About her is purely
Imaginary and any
Resemblance to actual
People living or dead
Is accidental my father
Collected chairs
She squeaks I’m
Rich he examined me
Designed a better
Light she adds
Lifting her legs
High he sees me
She says then still
Confidentially
But nothing here
Absolutely nothing
Should be confused
With the actual and
That’s my opening
